author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bookrunner Says Accelerated Bookbuilt Offering Of About 13 Mln Ordinary Shares Of Storebrand ASA
text:
Feb 20 (Reuters) - BOOKRUNNER:
* BLOCKTRADE - STOREBRAND ASA: BOOKRUNNER SAYS ACCELERATED BOOKBUILT OFFERING OF C.13 MILLION ORDINARY SHARES OF STOREBRAND ASA
* BLOCKTRADE - STOREBRAND ASA: BOOKRUNNER SAYS OFFERING OF ABOUT 13M SHARES REPRESENTING C.NOK 909M/ $116M BASED ON CLOSING PRICE OF NOK 69.96 ON FEB 20 Further company coverage: (Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
